name: x transpose
mathML_explicit:
<math display='block'>
 <msup intent='$op($arg)'>
  <mi arg='arg'>x</mi>
  <mi arg='op'
      intent='transpose'
      mathvariant='normal'>T</mi>
 </msup>
</math>

name: x transpose pre-sup

  <mprescripts/>

</math>

name: low (g∘h)′(x)
mathML_explicit:
<math display='block'>
 <mrow intent='$op3($x)'>
  <msup arg='op3' intent='$op2($composed)'>
   <mrow arg='composed' intent='$op1:infix($g,$h)'>
    <mo>(</mo>
    <mi arg='g'>g</mi>
    <mo arg='op1' intent='function-composition'>∘</mo>
    <mi arg='h'>h</mi>
    <mo>)</mo>
   </mrow>
   <mo arg='op2' intent='first-derivative'>′</mo>
  </msup>
  <mo>(</mo>
  <mi arg='x'>x</mi>
  <mo>)</mo>
 </mrow>
</math>

name: apply (g∘h)′(x)
mathML_explicit:
<math display='block'>
 <mrow intent='apply($op3,$x)'>
  <msup arg='op3' intent='apply($op2,$composed)'>
   <mrow arg='composed' intent='apply:infix($op1,$g,$h)'><!-- ?-->
    <mo>(</mo>
    <mi arg='g'>g</mi>
    <mo arg='op1' intent='function-composition'>∘</mo>
    <mi arg='h'>h</mi>
    <mo>)</mo>
   </mrow>
   <mo arg='op2' intent='first-derivative'>′</mo>
  </msup>
  <mo>(</mo>
  <mi arg='x'>x</mi>
  <mo>)</mo>
 </mrow>
</math>

name: leaf (g∘h)′(x)
mathML_explicit:
<math display='block'>
 <mrow>
  <msup intent='first-derivative($composed)'>
   <mrow arg='composed'>
    <mo>(</mo>
    <mi>g</mi>
    <mo intent='composed-with'>∘</mo>
    <mi>h</mi>
    <mo>)</mo>
   </mrow>
   <mo>′</mo>
  </msup>
  <mo>⁡</mo> <!-- apply function -->
  <mo>(</mo>
  <mi>x</mi>
  <mo>)</mo>
 </mrow>
</math>

        </mtd>

        </mtd>

         <mo>−</mo>
